<description><![CDATA[Come, Follow Me 2024 - July 1–7: “I Will Make an Instrument of Thee”]]></description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="body"><iframe class="IsolatedDom-sc-h3zeen-0 kmHRJp"/><p class="reference" data-aid="154411001" id="reference1">&#x201C;July 1&#x2013;7: &#x2018;I Will Make an Instrument of Thee.&#x2019; Alma 17&#x2013;22,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: Book of Mormon 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411002" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;July 1&#x2013;7. Alma 17&#x2013;22,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<header>
<figure class="image no-print" id="figure1">
