<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="body"><iframe class="IsolatedDom-sc-h3zeen-0 kmHRJp"/><p class="reference" data-aid="154411188" id="reference1">&#x201C;July 15&#x2013;21: &#x2018;The Virtue of the Word of God.&#x2019; Alma 30&#x2013;31,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: Book of Mormon 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411190" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;July 15&#x2013;21. Alma 30&#x2013;31,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<header>
<figure class="image no-print" id="figure1">
<div><div class="imageWrapper-wTPPD"><figure class="imageWithModal-ILaMF loadImageItem-u5D4D" title="Alma teaching Korihor"><img width="500" height="263" alt=""/><div class="container-W4jed"><div class="innerFlex-R9N_u"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="sc-1d18oav-0 bYvpFK"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M20 4.75L19.25 4v16l.75-.75H4l.75.75V4L4 4.75h16zM3.25 4v16c0 .414.336.75.75.75h16a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V4a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H4a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75zm11.07 8.888c.23-.357.606-.353.828-.008l2.887 4.482c.227.352.06.638-.357.638H6.326c-.421 0-.581-.3-.37-.648l4.006-6.622c.217-.358.567-.359.793.014l2.396 3.96 1.17-1.816zm1.59-2.735c1.14 0 2.066-.907 2.066-2.026 0-1.12-.926-2.027-2.067-2.027s-2.066.907-2.066 2.027c0 1.119.925 2.026 2.066 2.026z"> </path></svg><div class="description-Rip0y"><div class="sc-1szn76m-0 cRcVWO i18nString-raclU">Image</div><div class="sc-1szn76m-0 cRcVWO title-RrK9J">Alma teaching Korihor</div></div></div></div></figure></div></div>
