        " src="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/imgs/https%3A%2F%2Fassets.churchofjesuschrist.org%2F68%2F53%2F68530bdf7df9ba13bbd432041dcb03bd5195f49f%2F68530bdf7df9ba13bbd432041dcb03bd5195f49f.image%2Fjpeg/full/!250,/0/default"/><button aria-label="
                Play - Chapter 28: The Zoramites and the Rameumptom
            " class="sc-1g7hsbc-0 bCKkuP sc-bvqtyr-3 zrTrR" type="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="sc-1kfl9f7-0 hvmWVP"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M7.13 20.833c-.625.386-1.13.08-1.13-.678V3.845c0-.758.505-1.064 1.13-.678l13.401 8.155c.625.372.625.984 0 1.356l-13.4 8.155z"> </path></svg></button></div><div/></div></div>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="teaching-method" id="figure5">
<p data-aid="154411317" id="figure5_p1">For more ideas, see this month&#x2019;s issue of the <cite><a class="cross-ref" href="/study/friend/2024/07?lang=eng">Friend</a></cite> magazine.</p>
